Seriously though, most cultures in general have their  religions &quot;generic moral values&quot; imbedded in their minds already and understand why they are in place....I think we have come far enough as a species to be able to follow and pass down those values without having some guy tell us that an invisible man in the sky will fuck you up hardcore if you dont be a good. Some people say that &quot;it feels good to think that there is a greater power watching over us all&quot;, and to those people I say...Evolve, stop thinking like a fucking caveman, convincing yourself there is a god watching over you will have just the same effect on your life as wearing a charm around your neck or killing lambs on an alter...<br>
<br>
<br>
Done ranting about religion....sorry if I came off harsh, I live in baptist country and after years of having people &quot;posing&quot; to be my friends just so they can get close enough to try to convert me to their religion so they will look better in the eyes of their &quot;god&quot; has taken its toll on my spiritual values... <p><font color=RED>
